---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageWrapper from "../components/layouts/PageWrapper.astro";
---

<Layout title="Collaborate - KTTLSAA">
  <PageWrapper>
    <h1>Let's Collaborate</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      I'm always open to working with others on interesting projects, research initiatives, 
      or creative endeavors. Here are some ways we can collaborate:
    </p>
    
    <div class="collaboration-options">
      <section class="collab-section">
        <h2>Technical Projects</h2>
        <p>
          If you're working on a technical project related to knowledge management, 
          tools for thought, or web development, I'd be happy to contribute my skills and perspective.
        </p>
        <ul class="skill-list">
          <li>Web Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)</li>
          <li>Knowledge Graph Implementation</li>
          <li>Digital Garden Architecture</li>
          <li>User Experience Design</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      
      <section class="collab-section">
        <h2>Research Initiatives</h2>
        <p>
          I'm interested in collaborative research on topics including epistemology, 
          knowledge management, digital tools for thinking, and the intersection of technology and cognition.
        </p>
        <ul class="research-areas">
          <li>Personal Knowledge Management Systems</li>
          <li>Collaborative Learning Environments</li>
          <li>Digital Gardens as Knowledge Ecosystems</li>
          <li>Tools for Thought and Cognitive Enhancement</li>
        </ul